{"view":"article","slug":"4x4-4x4-yau","category":"4x4","subcategory":null,"topDir":"4x4","title":{"en":"4x4 Yau Method"},"content":{"en":"<p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/4x4-4x4-yau/en/image2.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong>4x4 Yau Method</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/4x4-4x4-yau/en/image4.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/4x4-4x4-yau/en/image6.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/4x4-4x4-yau/en/image8.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/4x4-4x4-yau/en/image10.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/4x4-4x4-yau/en/image12.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/4x4-4x4-yau/en/image14.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>F2C</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>F3E</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>L4C</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>LCE</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>L8E</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>3x3</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>Notation</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><strong>R</strong></p><p>Outer layer</p></td><td><p><strong>r</strong></p><p>2 layers</p></td><td><p><strong>2R</strong></p><p>Inner Slice</p></td><td><p><strong>3r</strong></p><p>3 layers</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/4x4-4x4-yau/en/image16.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/4x4-4x4-yau/en/image18.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/4x4-4x4-yau/en/image20.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/4x4-4x4-yau/en/image22.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>F2C (Two Opposite Center)</strong></p><p>See \"4x4 Redux\".</p><p><strong>F3E (Three Cross Edge)</strong></p><p>Hold white centers on L using z move. Put a white edge pair on 2L and 2R slices using outer layer moves, then pair them using r moves, then put the white stickers of this edge pair on L. Solve 2 more white edge pairs using the same procedure. Remember to pair and solve cross edges in correct relative positions.</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/4x4-4x4-yau/en/image24.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/4x4-4x4-yau/en/image26.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/4x4-4x4-yau/en/image28.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/4x4-4x4-yau/en/image30.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>r [U]</strong></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"r2 [U']\">r2 [U']</span></p></td><td><p><strong>1 solved</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>3 solved</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>L4C (Last Four Centers)</strong></p><p>During L4C, always place thumb and middle finger of left hand on front and back cross edges, resp. (assuming 3rd cross edge is at DL). Solve L4C using r, 3r, U-gen. Remember to solve centers into correct relative positions. Solve F center (3rd center), do x', solve current F center (4th center), do x', solve current F center (5th center), then 6th center will be solved automatically. One can also solve U center, then do x. Below is general idea on F center. Purple highlights immovable edge.</p><p><strong>Left Bar on F</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/4x4-4x4-yau/en/image32.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/4x4-4x4-yau/en/image34.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/4x4-4x4-yau/en/image36.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/4x4-4x4-yau/en/image38.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"3r U' 3r'\">3r U' 3r'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"3r U 3r'\">3r U 3r'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"3r 2r' U2 2r 3r'\">3r 2r' U2 2r 3r'</span></p></td><td><p><strong>Solved</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>F Center (r,U-gen)</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/4x4-4x4-yau/en/image40.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/4x4-4x4-yau/en/image42.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/4x4-4x4-yau/en/image44.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/4x4-4x4-yau/en/image46.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"r U2' r'\">r U2' r'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"r U r'\">r U r'</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"r U' r'\">r U' r'</span></p></td><td><p><strong>Solved</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>LCE (Last Cross Edge)</strong></p><p>Do z', and put LCE on E slice then pair them using flip algorithm. Then put them on D correctly.</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/4x4-4x4-yau/en/image48.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/4x4-4x4-yau/en/image50.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/4x4-4x4-yau/en/image52.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/4x4-4x4-yau/en/image54.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"u' (R U R') u\">u' (R U R') u</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"u' (R' F R F' R U' R') u\">u' (R' F R F' R U' R') u</span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"u2 (R U R') u2\">u2 (R U R') u2</span></p></td><td><p><strong>Solved</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>L8E 323 Method (Last Eight Edge)</strong></p><p>Do u', and put 3 edge pairs on E slice so that when doing u, 3 edge pairs are created. After this, use just 2 of <a href=\"/tutorial/f2l\" class=\"see-also-link\" data-see-also=\"true\">F2L</a> slots to pair up the remaining 5 edges, two or three at a time. </p><p><strong>Standard Example</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/4x4-4x4-yau/en/image56.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong>u</strong></p><p><em>Slice</em></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/4x4-4x4-yau/en/image58.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R U' R'\">R U' R'</span></p><p><em>Insert</em></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/4x4-4x4-yau/en/image60.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"L' U L y'\">L' U L y'</span></p><p><em>Insert</em></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/4x4-4x4-yau/en/image62.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"y' R U R' F R' F' R\">y' R U R' F R' F' R</span></p><p><em>Insert</em></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/4x4-4x4-yau/en/image64.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong>u</strong></p><p><em>Slice</em></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/4x4-4x4-yau/en/image66.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R U' R'\">R U' R'</span></p><p><em>Insert</em></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/4x4-4x4-yau/en/image68.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong>u'</strong></p><p><em>Slice</em></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/4x4-4x4-yau/en/image70.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R U' R'\">R U' R'</span></p><p><em>Insert</em></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/4x4-4x4-yau/en/image72.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>u</strong></p><p><em>Slice</em></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/4x4-4x4-yau/en/image74.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"F R' F' R\">F R' F' R</span></p><p><em>Insert</em></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/4x4-4x4-yau/en/image76.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"u' U'\">u' U'</span></p><p><em>Slice</em></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/4x4-4x4-yau/en/image78.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"R U' R'\">R U' R'</span></p><p><em>Insert</em></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/4x4-4x4-yau/en/image80.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td><p><strong>u</strong></p><p><em>Slice</em></p></td><td><p><strong><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/4x4-4x4-yau/en/image82.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></strong></p></td><td></td><td></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>3x3</strong></p><p><a id=\"_Hlk5990075\"></a><strong>Parity Cases which are Impossible on 3x3</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><strong>OLL parity</strong></p><p>Odd flipped edges</p></td><td><p><strong>PLL parity</strong></p><p> Odd edge pair/corner swaps</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/4x4-4x4-yau/en/image84.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/4x4-4x4-yau/en/image86.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>(r U2' r' U2) r U2' (↓r U2 l'· U2) (r U2' r' U2) x'· U2' r2</strong></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"u2 2R2 u2 2R2 U2 2R2 [U2]\">u2 2R2 u2 2R2 U2 2R2 [U2]</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div>"},"algs":["r2 [U']","3r U' 3r'","3r U 3r'","3r 2r' U2 2r 3r'","r U2' r'","r U r'","r U' r'","u' (R U R') u","u' (R' F R F' R U' R') u","u2 (R U R') u2","R U' R'","L' U L y'","y' R U R' F R' F' R","F R' F' R","u' U'","u2 2R2 u2 2R2 U2 2R2 [U2]"],"thumb":"/stats/tutorial/media/4x4-4x4-yau/en/image2.svg","warningCount":1,"hasImages":true,"hasTables":true}
